title: Beneath The Planet Of The Apes 1970  with greek subs.avi
description:
Beneath The Planet Of The Apes 1970  with greek subs.avi




O astronayths mprent exei stalthei gia na sosh ton teilor, alla ki aytos xanei ton elegxo kai prosgeionetai anomala ston planhth ton pithikon. O teilor einai xamenos sthn apagoreymenh zonh ki o mprent mazi me thn nova ton anazhtoyn.Prota tha synanthsh mia omada anthropon,oi opoioi zoyn me ton tromo ton neon stratiotikon kinhseon ton pithikon. H maxh den mporei na apofeyxthei ki o mprent vrisketai sth mesh.
